<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cn">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport"
        content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=2.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <meta name="keywords" content="">
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <title>403</title>
    <style>
        html,
        body,
        div,
        h1,
        h2,
        p {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0
        }

        img {
            border: none
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none
        }

        body {
            background-color: #fff;
            font-family: 微软雅黑;
            color: #212121
        }

        .header {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #fff;
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .inner {
            width: 1000px;
            margin:0 auto;
        }
        .main .inner{
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding:30px 0;
        }

        .divcss5-right {
            width: 600px;
            height: 30px;
            float: right
        }

        .icon {
            background: url(data:image/png;base64,)no-repeat;
            width: 135px;
            height: 44px;
            float: left
        }

        .icon-span {
            display: inline-block;
            color: #727272;
            font-size: 30px;
            vertical-align: top;
            height: 44px;
            line-height: 44px
        }

        .main {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #f6f6f8;
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .main-inner {
            height: 176px;
            background: url(data:image/png;base64,)no-repeat 50% 50%;
        }

        .footer {
            width: 100%;
            padding-top: 40px
        }

        .footer p {
            color: #727272;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            height: 20px;
            line-height: 20px
        }

        .footer p i {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            -webkit-border-radius: 50%;
            -moz-border-radius: 50%;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: #727272;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            font-style: normal;
            vertical-align: middle;
            margin-right: 6px
        }
        .header .title{
            margin:80px 0 50px;
            padding:0 0 50px 150px;
            position:relative;
        }
        .header .title .icon{
            position:absolute;
            left:0;
            top:7px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="inner">
            <div class="title">
                <i class="icon"></i>
                <span class="icon-span">很抱歉，您提交的信息可能对站点造成威胁，此次访问被阻断，相关行为已记录</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="main">
        <div class="inner">
            <div class="main-inner"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <!-- <div class="inner">
            <p>访问信息：</p>
            <p><i>1</i>客户端IP:
            </p>
            <p>
                <i>2</i>访问域名:
            </p>
            <p><i>3</i>访问时间:</p>
            <p>截图提供给网站客服，为您的访问提供绿色通道，不再拦截。</p>
        </div> -->
        <div class="divcss5-right">
            <p>Powerd By iflytek Security</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>